title: Amtrak’s Great Dome Car returns to the Northeast for fall foliage runs
text:
Amtrak’s Great Dome Car returns to the Northeast for fall foliage runs Korky Vann Monday, September 28, 2015 comments 11 shares Tweet With Labor Day in the rearview window, fall foliage is just ahead. If you’re like me, you love the great colors of the season, but hate the bumper-to-bumper traffic on backed-up country roads.
There’s an interesting alternative that offers leaf-peepers, train lovers and history buffs an unusual vantage point for some of the Northeast’s most beautiful landscapes.
